# 💾 Otacon Autosave Tool for Unity

A lightweight, customizable editor tool to prevent progress loss. It automatically saves your scenes and assets at your preferred intervals, with visual feedback directly in the Editor.

---

## 🚀 Features

* **Automatic Saving:** Saves both your open scenes and project assets.
* **Custom Intervals:** Set the time (in minutes) that fits your workflow.
* **Visual Feedback:** Displays a notification with a custom image in the Scene View when a save occurs.
* **Editor Integrated:** No need to attach scripts to GameObjects; it runs globally in the Editor.

