## 🛠 Installation

1.  **Download the Package:** Go to the [Releases](link-to-your-release) page and download `OtaconAutosave.unitypackage`.
2.  **Import:** Assets -> Import Package

---

## 📖 How to Use

1.  Open the configuration window via the top menu: **Tools > Autosave Config**.
2.  **Toggle Enabled:** Turn the autosave on or off.
3.  **Interval:** Enter the minutes between saves (e.g., 5 or 10).
5.  Keep the window docked or closed; the tool will keep running in the background!
